<topic template="Default" status="Needs Review" modified="2026-05-04T11:47:56.262Z" lasteditedby="noorhbo" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title>自动油脂维护屏幕 (LUBE)</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading4">自动油脂维护屏幕 (LUBE)</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;">这是自动注油维护屏幕，显示每个轴/主轴的默认注油间隔时间和当前运行时间。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;">导航至自动注油维护屏幕， </para>
    <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[MENU]</text>。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">显示主菜单。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按下<text style="font-weight:bold;">[GREASE]</text>图标。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">显示自动润滑脂维护屏幕。</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:10px;"><image src="Auto Greasing Maintenance Screen (LUBE).png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="31.00%" width="384" height="290" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:center; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:16px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:159px left ;"><anchor id="Fig5.3" styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:11pt;"></anchor><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:11pt;">图 &lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER3=5%&gt;.&lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER%&gt; &#160; 自动润滑保养</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;"> 屏幕 (LUBE)</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">项目说明</text></para>
    <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">泵前进</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:14px; margin-left:21px;">这表示润滑脂泵正向状态已打开或关闭。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:19px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="3" colcount="2" style="border-width:0px; border-spacing:0px; border-collapse:collapse; cell-border-width:1px; border-color:#000000; border-style:solid; head-row-background-color:#dddddd; alt-row-background-color:none;">
      <thead style="vertical-align:middle">
        <td style="width:200px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px;"><text style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold;">说明</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:200px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px;"><text style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold;">含义</text></para>
        </td>
      </thead>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:200px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px;"><image src="Interlock active.png" scale="39.00%" width="30" height="29" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; width:200px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">状态 &apos;开启&apos;</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:200px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px;"><image src="Interlock inactive.png" scale="39.00%" width="28" height="28" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; width:200px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">状态 &apos;关闭&apos;</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="2" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">压力高（LS2089）</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-left:21px;">这表示润滑脂压力开关处于打开或关闭状态。</para>
    <list id="3" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="3" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; page-break-before:always; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; page-break-before:always;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">初始填充数量</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:5px; margin-left:21px;">在初始满油模式下，需要在该字段中设置在初始满油模式下运行的注油循环次数。例如，如果该设置值为 &quot;2&quot;，则将在初始加注模式下运行两个周期（加注周期间隔为 2 分钟）。之后将返回正常注油模式（注油周期间隔为 960 分钟）。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:5px; margin-left:21px;">初始注油模式是以较短的间隔（2 分钟间隔）为机床注油。 </para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:14px; margin-left:21px;">更换润滑脂供应装置或管道后必须进行初始注油。</para>
    <list id="4" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="4" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">操作模式</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:21px;">它显示注油周期的当前状态。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:21px;">该字段显示的状态如下。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:21px;">待机 - 激活注油循环，间隔计时器运行。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:21px;">正常注油模式 - 激活正常注油周期，注油周期之间的间隔时间为 960 分钟。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:14px; margin-left:21px;">初始注油模式 - 激活初始注油模式，注油周期之间的间隔时间为 2 分钟。</para>
    <list id="5" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="5" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">下一个周期的时间</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:14px; margin-left:21px;">该字段显示下一个周期（下一次注油）的时间。</para>
    <list id="6" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="6" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">泵暂停时间</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:21px;">显示注油周期的间隔时间。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:21px;">该值因注油模式而异。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:21px;">正常模式 - 960 分钟。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:14px; margin-left:21px;">初始注油模式 - 2 分钟。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">按键说明</text></para>
    <list id="7" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="7" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">输入</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:14px; margin-left:21px;">要更改数值，需要按此软键激活输入模式。</para>
    <list id="8" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="8" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">INI 模式</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:21px;">要激活初始填充模式，请按此软键。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:14px; margin-left:21px;">当初始填充模式启用时，要关闭初始填充模式，请再次按下此软键。</para>
    <list id="9" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="9" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">重置</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:21px;">这是为了重置泵的计数值。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-left:21px;">按下此键后，泵的计数值将设置为 &apos;0&apos;。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:21px; page-break-before:always;"></para>
  </body>
</topic>
